      "description": "Available for your consideration is a driver-focused E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This high-revving 3.2L inline-six utilizes individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing to deliver linear power up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from a reinforced rear subframe and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. Recent service includes a comprehensive valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul, ensuring the mechanical integrity matches its visceral performance. While showing minor patina consistent with spirited use, the suspension geometry and drivetrain remain dialed for the enthusiast who values turn-in precision and instantaneous throttle response.",
